                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5180" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1302</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8353 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在疫情和油价双重大考中立稳踩实，心远路长——国际测井公司内部控制落地之惑 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to stand steadily and to keep making progress when facing the double challenges of the COVID-19 outbreak and low oil price? —International Logging Company’s confusion on implementing the internal control system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王瑞萍，楼旭明，赵晓铃，董影，杨婧姚，夏学锋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油集团长城钻探工程有限公司国际测井公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际测井公司；内部控制；有效性</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">International Logging Company; Internal Controls; Effectiveness</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠疫情在全球多地陆续进入暴发期，国际原油“减产联盟”谈判破裂，国际油价暴跌。在风云多变的国际市场环境下，走出国门的石油测井工程技术服务企业面临诸多挑战。长城钻探工程有限公司国际测井公司不仅着眼解决短期困境，更是谋求化被动为主动、强筋健骨的成长之道。本案例以国际测井公司内部控制体系落地困境为主线，重点描述其在新冠疫情和油价暴跌的双重压力下，管理层如何直面企业内部控制基础环境的缺陷以及对内部控制实施态度从被动到意识主动再到行为困惑的决策情境。如何处理好内部控制“设计有效”与“执行有效”的关系，找到内部控制的有效实施路径是壮志在心的国际测井公司提高国际化管理水平，防范国际经营风险，提高竞争软实力的当务之急。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The COVID-19 has broken out in many parts of the world, and the negotiations among members of the OPEC+ broke down. International oil prices plummeted. Under the changeable international market environment, the international oil logging service enterprises are facing numerous challenges. Facing the dual challenges of pandemic situation and low oil price, the International Logging Company of Great Wall Drilling Engineering Co., Ltd made much efforts. They not only aims to solve the short-term difficulties, but also seeks to turn the passive into the active and strong way of enterprises’ development, and actively plans the long-term growth in the future by focusing on the core competitiveness of the enterprise. Based on the dilemma of the predicament of International Logging Company&#39;s internal control system, this case focuses on the decision-making process of enterprise management team. Under the impact of COVID-19 and the sharp drop in oil prices, they face the defects of the basic environment for internal control of enterprises. Their attitude towards the implementation of internal control changed from passive to active and then to perplexity. The ambition of International Logging Companies is to improve their international management level, to prevent international business risks and to improve their competitive soft power. Their urgent affairs is how to deal with the relationship between &quot;effective design&quot; and &quot;effective implementation&quot; of internal control and to find the effective implementation path of internal control.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制》、《内部控制理论与实践》、《企业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-02</td>
                            </tr>
